.SH NAME
add_watch_to_object \- Add a watch on an object to a watch list
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" add_watch_to_object
.BI "(struct watch *watch "  ","
.BI "struct watch_list *wlist "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "watch" 12
The watch to add
.IP "wlist" 12
The watch list to add to
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\fIwatch->queue\fP must have been set to point to the queue to post notifications
to and the watch list of the object to be watched.  \fIwatch->cred\fP must also
have been set to the appropriate credentials and a ref taken on them.

The caller must pin the queue and the list both and must hold the list
locked against racing watch additions/removals.
